{"tid":2278618,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"吳文遠擺街站被控製造噪音　罪名不成立兼得訟費","createTime":"2020-11-09T09:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T11:55:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0324f3bb895a4140f0ab8dc6d87bd19bbbb70cb6","tid":2278618,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T09:24:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4291\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_info%2F4291&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BY%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=2a93c28b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_info/4291</a><br />\n<br />\n【頭條日報】社民連秘書長吳文遠今年5月在紅磡設街站要求政府因應疫情設立失業援助金，疑因「嗌咪」聲浪令途人感到不適，被票控擴音器造成的噪音煩擾罪。裁判官張天雁今午在九龍城裁判法院指出煩擾無清晰定義，控方亦未能提供相關證據，加上認為事主證供可信性成疑，故裁定吳文遠罪名不成立，並獲賠訟費。<br />\n<br />\n43歲被告吳文遠被票控於今年5月16日下午5時半，於紅磡德民街與紅磡道交界使用擴音器，造成男子姚永麟感到煩擾的根源。<br />\n<br />\n#20201109新聞"},{"pid":"597e7235910a14e06a499aa09ac3ba0970606f97","tid":2278618,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T11:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc26f8f96668a6a6f94279825c7b6792833e2ea8","tid":2278618,"uid":124382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"政府告你唔入，冇任何損失。堂費？  納稅人嘅錢嚟唧！"},{"pid":"d99ba5f23a8d6344e65032d0143b488493f33649","tid":2278618,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T11:55:15.000Z","msg":"等睇律政屍上訴 再上訴 無限上訴"}]}